LeetCode Submit Guard: Accidental Submit Blocker

Never face the frustration of accidental submissions on LeetCode again! Introducing LeetCode Submit Guard, the must-have Google Chrome extension for every coder. Our sophisticated plugin acts as a protective shield, ensuring that your hard work doesn't get submitted prematurely. Whether you're in the middle of a challenge or double-checking your solution, Submit Guard gives you peace of mind, allowing you to code with confidence. Enhance your LeetCode experience and say goodbye to unintended clicks. Install now and secure your code submissions like a pro!
Source code : https://github.com/ipogodin/LSG
